{
  "stem": "7598.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in unoccupied France, there were consulates and people who tried, people who tried to escape, tried to get there, and then hoped to be able to cross, either with a visa or on foot, the Pyrenees, get to Portugal, and perhaps find freedom there.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "From that moment onward, my uncle and aunt started thinking about trying to get away, to get out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was an extremely difficult decision to make, and my uncle quite understandably wasn't the, the bravest person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Life was fairly comfortable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We weren't wearing armbands yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We didn't have our passports stamped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And there weren't a lot of raids as then.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were raids on the diamond [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I don't think they were organized.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think there was just Germans ready to loot, because the Jews would throw their diamonds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the Germans would disappear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The, the raids and all the arrests, really, started in 1942.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, from about July 1940 to October 1941, which is when we did leave, we talked about it and weighed the pros and cons.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We wrote to my father and explained to him the dangers-- that is, if we were caught, we would be sent to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the chances are that one could be caught.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My father, of course, who was dying to see us again, was wise enough to say that he couldn't possibly take the responsibility for the decision.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The decision would have to be made by my uncle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had a young cousin of 20, one of whom survived, who--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was my father's sister's son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because he didn't have much responsibility, he dabbled a bit in the diamond business, in black marketeering.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
